1
00:00:03,033 --> 00:00:04,300
世上有两种痛苦
there are two kinds of pain

2
00:00:05,066 --> 00:00:06,633
一种让人变得坚强
sort of pain that makes you strong

3
00:00:07,466 --> 00:00:08,666
另一种则毫无意义
or useless pain

4
00:00:09,533 --> 00:00:11,333
只是徒添痛苦而已
sort of pain that's only suffering

5
00:00:12,400 --> 00:00:14,266
而我对无用之事毫无耐心
I have no patience for useless things

6
00:00:16,500 --> 00:00:19,000
像这样的时刻需要一个会行动的人
moments like this require someone who will act

7
00:00:20,600 --> 00:00:22,800
做不讨喜的事情
do the unpleasant thing

8
00:00:24,833 --> 00:00:26,066
同时也是必要的事情
the necessary thing

9
00:00:28,466 --> 00:00:30,400
我不管有多大代价
I don't care how much it hurts

10
00:00:30,400 --> 00:00:32,866
我不管有多大争议
I don't care how controversial it is

11
00:00:32,866 --> 00:00:35,233
你的任务，就是想办法做到
your job is to find a way

12
00:00:43,500 --> 00:00:45,633
你就是靠这种方式心安理得的吗
is this how you live with yourself

13
00:00:45,666 --> 00:00:49,000
把卑鄙当成体面
by rationalizing the obscene into the palatable

14
00:00:49,133 --> 00:00:52,833
通往权力之路，皆以牺牲铺就
the road to power is paved with casualties

15
00:00:53,333 --> 00:00:55,800
永不后悔
never regret
